CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 1, 1967, pg. 13, reads: "Hosted Regional - These members represent Kappa Chapter of Chi Eta Phi Sorority which entertained the North East Regional Conference. Left to right: Sorors Elsie Murray, Carrie Bullock, Dorothy Gambrell, Joyce Lomax, Mamie Garland and Marie Cowans."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of six Chi Eta Phi sorority members, two seated, in Howard Johnsons for sorority convention
